Patches for dst — dynamic suckless terminal
============================================

65 verified patches for dst (st 0.9.3 + 2 commits, commit 1694f5e).
All apply with patch -p1 -F0. Use with dst --rebuild include directives.

Source: https://st.suckless.org/patches/

Naming
  st-{category}.diff
  Map to st.suckless.org categories: st-foo-bar.diff → /patches/foo-bar/

Updating
  ./check-versions                   # list latest version of every category
  ./check-versions vertcenter        # check specific category

Notes
  - Colorscheme patches are superseded by dst runtime config
    (set colorN = #XXXXXX in ~/.config/dst/config)
  - xresources applies but conflicts with dst's config.c at link time;
    use xresources-reload instead
